Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.76,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}{\pos(162,361)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}交错的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上最大规模反联邦恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Break Pillar过去后4个月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多牺牲者与其家属的悲痛尚未散去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:15.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}非洲塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在Memento Mori的努力下 轨道升降机得以避免完全倒塌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩塌引起的异常气象也正出现平稳化趋向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 人类迎来了新的复兴之日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在联邦加盟国的技术支持下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲塔恢复输电
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这令人欢呼雀跃的日子 作为首任地球联邦总统 我在此宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在复兴的同时 新的战斗也将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防大型恐怖袭击于未然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:01:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦军将指挥权 归集于独立治安维持部队A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓为扑灭反联邦势力 实现真正的统一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遗余力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛内金上校的去向依旧不明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已增派保安局人员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 天人在宇宙出现?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道环上的Memento Mori 2号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打通道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是A-LAWS 防守好严密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚 协助她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子产生器的控制呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只协助这一次 如果是破坏卫星武器的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人攻陷了卫星武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS如果把注意力放在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的调查力度也会减缓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借此机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开饭 开饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了 别急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙盛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里又能挨多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道升降机一役后兵力不整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须卧薪尝胆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的监视日趋严密 谈何容易
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有天人在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果不行动 就不会有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我们就像身处无法挣扎的大漩涡中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:38.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}なくす事が拾うためなら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:43.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}別れるのは出逢うため
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:49.28,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}「さようなら」のあとには　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:55.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}「こんにちは」と出逢うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}緑色芝生…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:38.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}若失去是为了寻回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:43.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}别离就是为了相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:49.28,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}告别之后 一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:55.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}邂逅你的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7\fs18}多想躺在那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌是玛莉娜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在收音机中听到这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说几遍了 不许喊这名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是索玛·比利斯 超人机关的超兵一号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么上校必须死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台GN-X 是安德烈少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能下手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀自己的亲生父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 我是索玛 索玛·比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要却无法获得的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何能如此轻易地抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还向上校发誓再不让她参加战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时让她一个人呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要时间整理心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能让她冒险…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把自己的想法强加于她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在乎她的话就多些理解 她想参加战斗的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝也是相同心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把失去亲人的痛苦化作憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该对路易丝说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那的伤情如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以肩部伤口为中心 细胞代谢障碍正在扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拟GN粒子的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但进展非常缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拉塞先生的症状完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有某种抑制物在起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候如果能连接Veda的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿尔·萨谢斯 不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意图获得00的变革者的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 对方没有Twin Drive的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王牌 只有我的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人似乎重新开始活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实不相瞒 现在的情况令人很沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沮丧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报管制与增强军备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把旧时代的做法扩大到世界规模而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后作何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类没有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或早或晚让所有人类成为变革者?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时代正值变革期 必须割弃陈旧有害的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如旧时代人独揽财富与权力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居高临下藐视同族大众的思考方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是指桑骂槐?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是否情愿都会被时代所抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同你的美貌会随时间而流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往回到美不胜收的过去 伤害他人获得安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知不可取 却无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不认为得有人让他们领悟吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的价值观太过狭隘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以更广阔的视野思考事物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗 那么 期待能看到这广阔世界的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法成为变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很可悲 但这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么疏远她没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经失去了利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去照顾?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近来4个月 你们不是挺热乎的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打听天人的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就暂且算作如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说您荣升中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据判Break Pillar事件中\N我击坠的机体是政变的主谋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上层似乎做出了认可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会被你祝贺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害亲生父亲获得高升
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是A-LAWS的精英 大义灭亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了自己的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲投靠了叛乱分子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在履行自己的军务而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知是父亲吗 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为人们盼望结束纷争的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从军中叛逃 威胁政权的人必须得到正法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我亲手埋葬他 是我仅存的一点怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相同情况下 你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻夺走别人的生命 却无法对亲人下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男的弑父 女的想给家人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝配啊 你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果重视她 就必须由你去保护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 我们是在为理想而战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此有时需要做出抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今后也会面临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向沙慈开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找回路易丝·阿勒威 只有靠战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为找回她而战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军终于沦为A-LAWS的傀儡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光这4个月间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS就发动了近20次攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们太衰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事 敌人似乎能确定我们的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越衰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:14:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·诺列嘉 还是把作战行动付诸实施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda 联邦 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者肯定在利用Veda进行情报管制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要夺回Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键是找不到Veda的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无从下手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只能去问知道情报的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 难道问变革者?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 莱尔 能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从中学起就开始住校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要寄宿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想被人拿来和完美的哥哥比较
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起拼搏 选择了逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你和哥哥一样 成为了Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 从没听你说过 艾纽的家人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话不说就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽仍旧是艾纽 这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽 艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的中途别发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是里维夫 鼻子比狗还灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在表示谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂的联络呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用场的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 让舰船改变航向前往普特莱玛奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里维尔上尉来电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现天人 坐标ES8874
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有特许的两人也去助阵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队准备出击 MS队准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能坐上Ahead了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机能正常 GN Drive开始连接
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闸门开放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗 战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead第一小队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 阿勒威机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体的维护十分完备 你所称的奥义也加以强化了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心知肚明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学探测器捕捉到MS部队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离抵达战斗宙域0054
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按老规矩各就各位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 太能省了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 肩伤如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的MS部队 捕捉到总计12台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这么少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别轻敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人部队中有变革者的专用机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的部队中 有路易丝驾驶的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这四个月来 为重整战力 到处东躲西藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次应该要打了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:18:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算对路易丝开枪?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要看你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗并非只是破坏 也能创造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信 我们的Gundam能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法扣下扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能不断呼喊路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去找回路易丝·阿勒威吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 第1 第2 第3闸门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾迪先生 期待你的战果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 提耶利亚·艾迪 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
